{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act43side", "eventName": "紅絲絨", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AD-3", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "戲劇性", "storyInfo": "蒂比盤問最後見到謝莉的男主角邁克爾，認為他具有犯案嫌疑；與此同時，八卦攝影助理正在探尋盧西恩身上的秘密，卻意外得知了拍攝地塊即將遭遇天災的重磅消息。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g9_outsidestudio_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……謝莉小姐死了。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始是道爾頓，再是謝莉……我的天，這到底是怎麼一回事？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，謝莉小姐死了。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#3$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這是什麼口氣？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你專程來攔住我和邁克爾，通知我們劇組又出了意外，我們也很震驚。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉小姐死前見到的最後一個人，是邁克爾先生。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不要血口噴人，小蒂比。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉昨天明明參加了你的觀影會，和你還有莫伊拉待在一起，我都聽說了。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正因為昨晚謝莉小姐是和我們在一起，正因為她中途收到了一則訊息離開，我和莫麗沒有多問，也沒有陪她，後來出了那樣的事情……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以我和莫麗才必須調查清楚到底發生了什麼事情，我詢問了很多人——", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有工作人員看到了，她在離那個倉庫不遠的攝影棚和你碰面了！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是偶遇！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看她一副魂不守舍的樣子，以為她還在為中斷拍攝的事感到愧疚，想安慰她一下。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，沒想到她真的想不開。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安慰，攝影棚，就你們兩個？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，相信我。我心裡只有你一個。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴！", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#5$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，真的是你殺了謝莉？", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "才幾天而已，就發生了兩起意外？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且都鬧出人命了。藍卡塢那麼多劇組徵人，我怎麼偏偏挑了這個地方，唉，真倒楣……", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#2$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了好了。無故翻倒的油漆桶，攝影棚外竄過的黑影，甚至連城際網路訊號失靈，你都能怪自己的運氣差。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我反而覺得是我們太幸運了！事故現場的一手資料能在娛樂週刊賣出一筆好價錢——", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓開一點，我看不清謝莉遺體的細節了。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別看了……我們得去攝影棚幫忙了。", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先去，霍汀。我得把這些都記下來！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "倒楣的場務"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1846_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_penrustle"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……聽阿布納說，謝莉以前就神經兮兮的。難道是道爾頓的死對她的衝擊太大，所以自尋短見？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "合理但略顯無聊。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是另有隱情……嘿嘿，那我上半年的房租都不用苦惱了，誰還要當整天舉麥克風收音桿的人形支架啊！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫療小組不是說謝莉是被凍死的嗎，那她的左手掌心怎麼有那麼多傷口？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶——看起來真恐怖，難道是某種詛咒儀式……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並非詛咒，而是自我掙扎的痕跡。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……掙扎？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉不是精神壓力過大，自暴自棄才走進冷凍庫的嗎？難道真的有內幕——", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生！你走路怎麼沒聲音啊！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以疼痛抵抗幻覺，是我提出的建議。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉小姐耳中迴響著往事的遺音，但她仍想完成自己的工作，為電影帶來圓滿的結局。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不會因絕望尋死，自傷的血痂就是最好的印證。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是這次，疼痛沒能引她逃脫幻境。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#4$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個固執、神經質、難以溝通的謝莉聽從了你提出的建議？真難以置信……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你似乎很瞭解她啊，盧西恩先生。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不算很瞭解。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "62_g9_outsidestudio_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼跟什麼啊！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我告白失敗就殺了謝莉？親愛的，你怎麼會想到這種無稽之談？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊對了對了，小蒂比，你剛剛不是說謝莉是突然接到了一則訊息離開的嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當時也注意到她拿著終端。所以，一定是那個給她傳訊息的人誘殺了她，對吧？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道那個人不是你？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也需要一個解釋，邁克爾。", "name": "瑪麗昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然冷凍庫的低溫環境導致終端損壞，記錄已經無法修復，但我們的終端都是劇組統一提供的，只有同組成員在聯絡名單裡……", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有完沒完啊！蒂比大偵探？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道就不能是格蕾塔女士，或者是米蘭妮女士嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "白天她打斷了拍攝，這兩位都很不高興，說不定是想再教訓一下謝莉。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "格蕾塔女士和謝莉小姐在工作時形影不離，有很多可以處理突發事件的機會。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米蘭妮女士嚴格遵守片場的禮儀和規則，她尊重劇組安排的日程，不會在休息時間打擾其他成員。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從目前得知的情況看來，我們只知道，出事前她見過你。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，我根本不知道誰傳訊息給她，我只是剛好在攝影棚遇到她而已！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個時間點，通常你不是在自助酒吧跟美術組的姐姐喝酒，就是在瑪麗昂的房間裡。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夜晚對你來說是非常寶貴的時間，對吧？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁克爾先生，你為什麼會回到拍攝區？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，可愛的小鳥，你是因為不能跟我一起喝酒所以不高興了嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等你再長大一點，我們會有機會的——", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你因為某種目的來到攝影棚。你遇見為了赴約離開道具間的謝莉。如果你真的只是對她說了幾句安慰的話，為什麼不肯正面回答我的所有問題？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝莉的死，真的跟你沒關係？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼，蒂比，在藍卡塢的各處體驗不同的工作類型——雜務、場務、布景、噴畫師……還不夠滿足你，現在又想當偵探了嗎？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是說一部恐怖電影就把謝莉變成你和莫伊拉的姐妹小團體的新成員了？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別裝了。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工作的時候，她也很常對著你亂塗亂畫的陰森布景背板破口大駡，你們根本不熟，幹嘛現在咬著我不放？", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有意外背後都有真兇？電影看多了吧！", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……認識謝莉小姐的兩個月以來，她很少對劇組成員微笑，也很少讚美別人。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她指責我的次數最多，為了改出我們都能接受的背景繪圖，我加班了很多次。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我知道她檢查每天的拍攝素材時，會展露欣喜的神情；那些異想天開的布景背板裡致敬了多少小眾影片，只有她能看出來。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果她真的已經非常非常痛苦想要解脫……我會尊重她的決定。", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但如果有人在控制她的情緒，摧殘她的心智，剝奪她繼續熱愛電影的權利，我無法原諒！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我跟謝莉確實是偶遇。昨天晚上我去攝影棚……是為了找人。", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找人？誰能為你作證！", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1838_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "邁克爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我。", "name": "？？？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1839_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫麗？", "name": "蒂比"}, "figure_art": "avg_4191_tippi_1#8$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "昨天晚上，邁克爾先生是來找我的。", "name": "莫伊拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1831_1#1$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_warehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你跟謝莉小姐走得很近？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是對她的痛苦感同身受。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她有必須保持清醒的理由，我也是。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）神秘詛咒，還是因愛生恨……哪種方向的八卦更受讀者歡迎呢……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳，那昨天晚上你在哪裡？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二樓辦公室。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得那間辦公室是謝莉和格蕾塔存放重要文件的地方，你去那裡做什麼？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解謎。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誰能幫你作證？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Miss.Christine。", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，你要我相信跟在你身邊的那隻小怪物？她都不會開口說話！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#6$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#7$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩先生，別露出這種不悅的表情嘛……", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看過你那天和道爾頓對戲，知道你是一名多麼出色的演員……偽裝坦誠，對你來說不是難事。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實在的，我個人一點也不關心謝莉因何而死，也就是說，即使她的死真的與你有關，我也絕對不會向警方檢舉。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甚至，如果你登上不入流的八卦小報，警察還會降低對你的懷疑度——沒人相信花邊新聞說的是真的，大多只是當笑話看。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以請你再配合我一下——你在辦公室解的謎到底是什麼？難道是在策劃如何讓謝莉掉入陷阱？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你絲毫不懼移動地塊上正在發生謀殺案？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，劇組裡的恩怨情仇數不勝數……不然我靠什麼吃飯？當攝影助理嗎？", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#2$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕謎題的答案會威脅到所有人的生命？", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#2$1"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈！誇大其辭。", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那請你保守秘密……", "name": "盧西恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1828_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然！我才不會讓別人分我的獨家稿費呢！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#5$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "盧西恩靠近攝影助理的耳朵，輕柔地吐露被隱瞞的真相。"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "攝影助理的眼神從興奮轉為驚恐。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_pendrop"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "八卦專用筆記本和筆掉落在地，豐蹄爆發出的驚呼響徹整個倉庫。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "仍在清理現場的劇組成員不滿地看向盧西恩和攝影助理，下一秒，一則駭人聽聞的訊息傳入每個人的耳中。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說這個地塊很有可能即將遭遇天災？！", "name": "攝影助理"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1844_1#3$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}